'''Jeswandi''' was an ancient art of [[Meditation/Legends|meditation]] and martial arts among the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] people. [[Girov Dza'tey]] mastered it, and that ability allowed him to overcome the power of the [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] [[Sith temple/Legends|Temple]] on [[Malrev IV]]. He later used Jeswandi to harness the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark power]] of the temple in an attempt to destroy [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]].

